items.title: What to know about the Sugar Bowl 2025
items.description: The Sugar Bowl, postponed after a tragic New Year's Day terror attack in New Orleans, will now kick off today at 3 p.m. CST.

items.title: Authorities search for motive in deadly New Orleans attack
items.description: One day after a man drove a truck into New Year's revelers on Bourbon Street, law enforcement is searching for possible accomplices.

items.title: Authorities search Houston location linked to New Orleans truck attacker
items.description: The FBI said it searched a location in Houston in connection to the New Orleans truck attack that killed 15 people.
